<p>&#8220;It&#8217;s an uncontroversial commercial, perhaps the lamest one I&#8217;ve directed so far. There&#8217;s not even any nudity,&#8221; Qang said during his <i>&#8220;Free Photo-shoots for Kids&#8221;</i> tour in Asia.</p>
<p>&#8220;Everyone loved the Platinum commercial, and that one focuses on deadly weapons. It goes to say that people approve more of killing than they do something as natural and beautiful as making love,&#8221; Goldman said about the <a title="Alpha Consumer Platinum Card" href="/services/alpha-consumer-platinum-card/">Alpha Consumer Platinum Card</a> commercial, which still hasn&#8217;t been banned from <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tghT6dYLRvA" target="_blank">YouTube</a>.</p>
